---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
    <section class="pt-24 pb-16 px-6 bg-white min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#423c3b] mb-6 leading-tight">
                Chauchilla Necropolis + Pottery + Weaving Workshop
            </h1>
            <img src="/chauchilla.avif" alt="NecrÃ³polis de Chauchilla" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-8" />

            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 text-lg">
                <p>
                    This tour includes:
                </p>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#423c3b]">
                            <i class="fas fa-skull-crossbones mr-2 text-[#a59f89]"></i>
                            Chauchilla Necropolis:
                        </h2>
                        <p>
                            Delve into this ancient pre-Hispanic cemetery, located in the heart of the Nazca Desert. Preserved by the dry climate, the tombs house mummies, ceramics, and funerary remains that reveal the ancestral beliefs and practices of the Nazca culture. A specialized guide will explain the historical context and the most important archaeological finds.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#423c3b]">
                            <i class="fas fa-paint-brush mr-2 text-[#a59f89]"></i>
                            Traditional Ceramics Workshop:
                        </h2>
                        <p>
                            Visit a local workshop where artisans reproduce ancestral Nasca pottery techniques. You'll see how pieces are shaped and painted following original designs. You'll also have the opportunity to participate and create your own piece, taking home a handmade souvenir.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#423c3b]">
                            <i class="fas fa-hands mr-2 text-[#a59f89]"></i>
                            Weaving Workshop:
                        </h2>
                        <p>
                            Immerse yourself in Nasca textile art with a live demonstration of the spinning, dyeing, and weaving process using natural fibers. Learn about the symbols and colors used by the ancient Nasca and how these techniques survive through oral transmission and the work of local communities.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base pt-4">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Approximate duration:</strong> 3 hours
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Departure from:</strong> City of Nasca
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Includes:</strong> Tourist transportation, Tickets to the sites, Local guide, Participation in both workshops.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <div class="pt-4">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">
                        <i class="fas fa-sun mr-2 text-[#a59f89]"></i>
                        Recommendations:
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base">
                        <li>Bring a hat, sunscreen, and water.</li>
                        <li>Wear comfortable shoes.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-10">
                    <a href="/#tours" class="text-[#423c3b] px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-[#423c3b] text-base font-medium hover:bg-[#423c3b] hover:text-[#cbc4ae] transition">
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i> Back to Itineraries
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://wa.link/0voy2n" class="bg-[#423c3b] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-base font-medium hover:bg-[#3d3433] transition" target="_blank">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i>
                        Request Reservation
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
